Package: webfilter
Version: @VERSION@
Section: net
Priority: optional
Architecture: @ARCH@
Depends: systemd
Maintainer: Yjlion <noreply@users.noreply.github.com>
Homepage: https://github.com/Yjlion/mitmproxy-web-filter
Description: MITM-intercepting forward proxy with per-client filtering policies
 WebFilter Proxy is a from-scratch Go port of mitmproxy-web-filter: a
 MITM-intercepting forward proxy with per-client filtering policies and a
 browser-based management UI, shipped as a single static binary. Installs
 to /opt/webfilter, seeds config/settings.json and policies/default.json
 from the bundled examples if missing, and enables (but does not start)
 webfilter.service - see postinst output for next steps.
